social_posts.post_text: 🌸SOL DE JENEIRO CHEIROSA 68🌸 Spring PERFECTION - my current obsession 🥰 #soldejeneiro #soldejeneiro68 #cheirosa68

hello there 👋🏻it’s been so long since I posted a selfie on here… I feel like I had to post something since the earlier colorful looks I have on here are definitely in my makeup past 😆 My love for no-makeup makeup look came back and I re-focused again on more simple.. glowing & radiant skin ☺️ 

I’ve been blessed to be able to work remotely from home here in England 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿 and raising my two boys has kept me very busy but I still do love and buy makeup and I’m hoping I will go back to reviewing again! I miss all of my online friends and I always try to at least leave a like on some of the posts if I am scrolling through my feed. So I see you and your awesome work my fellow beauty content creators😘😍 

happy Sunday everyone!☀️

🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿 York - England’s most haunted city 👻 Shambles - very climatic, historic street featuring medieval buildings as well as some really cool stores (York Ghost Merchants was my favorite). But gosh it was so extremely crowded you could barely pass by. If we ever go back, we would probably skip the weekend and try to visit during the week ☺️ Their market looked incredible as well! #yorkengland #yorkghostmerchants

🏴󠁧󠁢󠁳󠁣󠁴󠁿🏰 We had the absolute best time visiting stunning Edinburgh with its cobblestone sidewalks and beautiful rustic cityscape 😍 Our apartment was located right in the heart of Royal Mile so it was perfect for the kids as everything was a short walk from it. We hope to be back one day!🤍
